metaTags.metaTitle: Cloudflare Free SSL/TLS | Get SSL Certificates
metaTags.metaDescription: Cloudflare offers free SSL/TLS certificates to secure your web traffic. Improve performance and save time on TLS certificate management with Cloudflare.

promotionalBanner.desktopText: Not sure what SSL is or how to use it? Read more in our Learning Center.

psaBanner.text: Simplify management by auto-renewing all certificates on all your domains with DCV delegation

relatedBlades.title: SSL/TLS certificates
relatedBlades.subtitle: Fast, easy, free TLS certificates for websites
relatedBlades.copy: Protect users and data without slowing down web apps by relying on Cloudflare for TLS. Save time on TLS certificate management and keep certificates up to date to avoid browser security warnings and search engine deprioritization.

features.title: Improve Website Performance
features.description: Cloudflare's modern SSL improves webpage load times to provide a better visitor experience on your website.

features.title: Protect Website Visitors
features.description: Encrypting traffic with TLS ensures nobody can snoop on your users' data and is  crucial in complying with data privacy regulations across the globe.

features.title: Boost traffic to your website
features.description: Search engines like GoogleÂ®, favor websites encrypted with TLS in search result rankings. Avoid browser warnings present on unencrypted sites that dissuade users from visiting.

features.title: Deploy effortlessly
features.description: Set up certificates for a domain in less than 5 minutes. Keep your hosting provider. No code changes required.

relatedBlades.title: Trusted by the world's biggest brands
relatedBlades.copy: %{Fortune1000Percentage} of Fortune 1000 companies rely on Cloudflare

relatedBlades.quote: "Using Cloudflare's TLS certificates, which automatically renew, we save about $50,000 a year, both in administrative costs and lost revenue from outages due to expired certificates."

quoteCarousel.quote: "I can just tell Cloudflare, 'this is the SSL certificate authority that we use.' Cloudflare picks it up from there, and they take care of the deployment of the certificates. Which is great because I don't have to worry about it anymore. It's just a one-time thing."

image.description: Mount Pleasant Independent School District logo

quoteCarousel.quote: "Cloudflare helps DHL Parcel protect our customer data and client communications, simplifying compliance with data privacy regulations like GDPR."

planFeatures.name: Web Application Firewall (WAF)
planFeatures.description: Cloudflare Web Application Firewall's intuitive dashboard enables users to build powerful rules through easy clicks and also provides Terraform integration. Every request to the WAF is inspected against the rule engine and the threat intelligence curated from protecting millions of websites. Suspicious requests can be blocked, challenged or logged as per the needs of the user while legitimate requests are routed to the destination, agnostic of whether it lives on-premise or in the cloud.
